{"tid":1825031,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"[減肥撚] 入嚟傾吓飲食餐單","createTime":"2020-01-15T02:44:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T11:14:34.000Z","uid":206613,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"647a12c47675a6a931bdaf5ea130812950e27c8a","tid":1825031,"uid":206613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:44:41.000Z","msg":"夏天就到 目標兩個月減6至8KG (減脂<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>飲食控制</ins></strong><br />\n1000至1300kcal<br />\n自己煮多 平時食開蛋雞胸西蘭花糙米飯 <br />\n星期六日有時同朋友出去食就無戒口<br />\n集中揀蛋白質同纖維為主嘅嘢食 <br />\ne.g. 牛肉/豆腐/菜<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>運動</ins></strong><br />\n一個星期五至七日有氧 三至五日重訓<br />\n有氧多數跑步 30至60分鐘 10km/hr<br />\n重訓做腳同core為主 大概每part做4至8 sets<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>之前記錄 </strong></ins><br />\n一個星期四至五日有氧 兩日重訓<br />\n<br />\n利申 呢兩年先開始做返運動 <br />\n<br />\n有無人係蛋奶素餐單分享下?<br />\n我想新一年轉食素<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5860b16c79f204b219cfc8b516516f35a81bf2cb","tid":1825031,"uid":152584,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:54:39.000Z","msg":"細蚊仔?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該減唔到"},{"pid":"ac99e43dde51cdf1d883ba434b649edcca81929d","tid":1825031,"uid":131036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:56:35.000Z","msg":"本身幾重 幾多體脂先"},{"pid":"285e42d270c6f51c2c2551190fa3e170803176e3","tid":1825031,"uid":206613,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"ac99e43dde51cdf1d883ba434b649edcca81929d","tid":1825031,"uid":131036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:56:35.000Z","msg":"本身幾重 幾多體脂先"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T03:24:01.000Z","msg":"體脂26%<br />\n體重48KG<br />\n身高 160cm"},{"pid":"1ccb6bceac6fb03001ef829fcd9c2f3689725b1b","tid":1825031,"uid":206613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5860b16c79f204b219cfc8b516516f35a81bf2cb","tid":1825031,"uid":152584,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:54:39.000Z","msg":